raspberry pi gcc c kodu çalıştırma
https://www.circuitbasics.com/how-to-write-and-run-a-c-program-on-the-raspberry-pi/
sudo nano hello-world.c
kodu yaz
gcc hello-world.c -o myfirstcprogram
chmod +x myfirstcprogram
./myfirstcprogram
